Title: The Hopf Algebra Structure of Connes and Kreimer in Epstein-Glaser

RenormalizationAuthors: G. Pinter

Comments: 8 pages

Journal-ref: Lett.Math.Phys. 54 (2000) 227-233

We show how the Hopf algebra structure of renormalization discovered byKreimer can be found in the Epstein-Glaser framework without using an analogueof the forest formula of Zimmermann.